#Packet sniffer

Packet sniffer a simple packet sniffer application based on libpcap that displays packet information. Program has to be run as root user.

### Included files
 - ipk-sniffer.c
 - Makefile
 - manual.pdf
 - README

### Compile the program

```sh
$ make
```

### Usage information
```sh
$ ./ipk-sniffer -h
```

### Run the program
```sh
$ ./ipk-sniffer -i interface [-p port] [--tcp|-t] [--udp|-u] [-n num]\n
```
